### ===== Control Plane API =====

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health

### List all registered capabilities
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/capabilities

### Register a capability
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/capabilities/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "capability_id": "stallion.retrieve_invoice_details",
  "name": "retrieve_invoice_details",
  "description": "Retrieves invoice details from Oracle Accounts Receivable",
  "tags": ["oracle", "invoice", "finance"],
  "agent_id": "stallion-cash-matching",
  "idempotent": true,
  "side_effects": false,
  "endpoint": {
    "method": "GET",
    "path": "/invoices/{invoice_id}",
    "arguments": {
      "invoice_id": { "in": "path" }
    },
    "response": { "from": "body" }
  },
  "proxy_url": "http://localhost:3501"
}

### Discover capabilities
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/discover
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "Match invoice INV-4821 to cash receipt for customer CUST-4821",
  "max_tools": 20
}

### Discover by tag
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/discover
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": ["finance"],
  "max_tools": 10
}

### Invoke a capability (CP returns proxy route info)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/invoke/stallion.retrieve_invoice_details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "arguments": {
    "invoice_id": "INV-4821"
  },
  "caller_id": "stallion-agent",
  "goal_id": "GOAL-001"
}

### Send heartbeat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent_id": "stallion-cash-matching",
  "capability_ids": ["stallion.retrieve_invoice_details"]
}

### Health - capabilities breakdown
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health/capabilities

### Unregister a capability
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/capabilities/stallion.retrieve_invoice_details


### ===== Proxy API (Agent Mode) =====

### Discover via proxy
POST http://localhost:3500/api/v1/discover
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "Match invoice INV-4821 to cash receipt",
  "max_tools": 20
}

### Invoke via proxy
POST http://localhost:3500/api/v1/invoke/stallion.retrieve_invoice_details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "arguments": {
    "invoice_id": "INV-4821"
  },
  "caller_id": "stallion-agent",
  "goal_id": "GOAL-001",
  "tenant_id": "stallion"
}

### Proxy health
GET http://localhost:3500/api/v1/health
